OL,5, French supermarket Carrefour has put   
OL,6, stickers on its shelves this week      
OL,7, warning shoppers of "shrinkflation" -  
OL,8, where packet contents are getting      
OL,9, smaller while prices are not.          
OL,11,FLipton Ice Tea, Lindt chocolate and    
OL,12,FViennetta ice cream are among the      
OL,13,Fproducts being named and shamed.       
OL,15,FShoppers are being told if bottles are 
OL,16,Fsmaller or pack contents lighter.      
OL,18,FCarrefour said it wanted to put        
OL,19,Fpressure on the firms making the       
OL,20,Fproducts to keep prices down.          
